Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.37,0:01:38.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禁斷皇帝 阿圖爾·賈茲…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.74,0:01:41.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其女兒將是他的繼承人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.54,0:01:43.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同時…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.84,0:01:45.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是肩負命運之人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.07,0:01:47.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命運?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.52,0:01:50.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡的存在 僅僅是個開始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.09,0:01:56.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前方等待的是超乎人們想象的命運…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.28,0:02:02.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你 不過是件推動命運的工具罷了

Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.35,0:02:10.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,背著棺材的少女

Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.34,0:02:22.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不能乾脆哪裡掉著錢嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.28,0:02:32.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兔子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.94,0:02:34.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我拿你下鍋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.52,0:02:41.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.11,0:02:44.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在這深山裡搞什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.25,0:03:00.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,襲…襲擊?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.69,0:03:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰襲擊? 襲擊誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.92,0:03:05.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劫…劫路賊?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.31,0:03:07.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉你又猜錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.58,0:03:10.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正處於無業中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.18,0:03:13.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒吃的東西果腹 所以跑來挖野菜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.91,0:03:15.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,窮人?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.02,0:03:17.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.24,0:03:20.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,領會 無業窮人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.19,0:03:22.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒說錯但令人火大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.73,0:03:25.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你又在這種地方干什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.71,0:03:28.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那東西是棺材嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.17,0:03:31.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山 無人 好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.52,0:03:33.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.57,0:03:37.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 這個 假裝沒看到 沒見過 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.99,0:03:39.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那棺材裡裝了實物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.93,0:03:42.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難不成…你是個殺人犯?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.93,0:03:43.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罪人 不是!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:46.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旅人! 柔弱的旅人!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.46,0:03:48.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目的地 戴爾索蘭特市
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.75,0:03:51.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無比遙遠…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.21,0:03:53.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在這山裡走多久了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.64,0:03:56.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.67,0:03:59.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般哪用走那麼久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.19,0:04:01.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明顯迷路了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:04.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,震驚的事實
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.63,0:04:07.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你身上有錢不?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:09.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小偷! 窮人! 劫路賊!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.05,0:04:13.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 我是想你請我吃早飯我替你帶路啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.34,0:04:18.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以神不知鬼不覺地將你帶進城裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.74,0:04:22.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然看你這樣子 一輩子也別想走下山啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.78,0:04:35.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獨角馬…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.83,0:04:38.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋…倒霉透了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.11,0:04:30.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Moruzerun Moruzerun Emurun
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.40,0:04:34.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Zeburun Wamurun Tourun
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.55,0:04:41.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.34,0:04:48.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 這玩意兒丟掉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.90,0:04:51.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拒絕 接觸不得 貴重品!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.49,0:04:52.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥? 什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.96,0:04:55.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 沒辦法 我收回前言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.22,0:04:57.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那棺材可千萬別放手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:05:01.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs43\shad0\pos(640,660)}Moruzerun Moruzerun
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.91,0:05:01.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.69,0:05:08.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跳!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.90,0:05:19.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想被它吃掉 就給我抓緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.56,0:05:27.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了 肚子餓得使不出力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.00,0:05:30.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然 強硬 亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.61,0:05:32.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.98,0:05:33.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包紮 緊急
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.23,0:05:39.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才那是獨角馬 它不用多久還會襲來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.35,0:05:42.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有 包扎 不能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.42,0:05:47.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對甩不掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.10,0:05:50.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是 無趣的一生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.53,0:05:51.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放棄?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.31,0:05:52.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.76,0:05:54.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要死?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.76,0:05:55.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估計是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.31,0:05:57.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死亡 不畏懼?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.78,0:06:01.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要說真一點不怕 那是瞎話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.88,0:06:03.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我活著也沒什麼可幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.65,0:06:07.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這樣的世界裡 我就是個廢物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.26,0:06:21.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,機杖?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.73,0:06:23.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來你是魔法師啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.22,0:06:24.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.96,0:06:27.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,廢物 同樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.70,0:06:29.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 只會這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.75,0:06:31.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他 廢物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.80,0:06:34.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但這個 能辦到 很多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.89,0:06:37.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如 幹掉獨角馬?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.05,0:06:39.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要 時間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.95,0:06:43.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法術式 起動中 移動 不能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.63,0:06:48.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拖延時間就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.08,0:06:51.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要爭取到時間 你就能用魔法了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.75,0:06:52.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:02.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我為鋼也
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.04,0:07:06.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鋼故不怯 鋼故不惑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.47,0:07:09.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦逢敵 盡無一切躊躇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.07,0:07:11.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為滅此兇器也
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.70,0:07:13.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鐵血轉化
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.24,0:07:22.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Zeburun Wamurun Tourun
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.96,0:07:30.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來啊 駑馬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.95,0:08:03.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kokult elum Naikt inte Naint kum
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.73,0:08:12.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ee wam ee wam milta ru Kokult elum
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.05,0:08:14.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.81,0:08:26.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Naikt inte naint
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.86,0:08:38.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Milta ru
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.41,0:08:40.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利刃呀奔流吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.01,0:08:42.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The Ripper
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.61,0:09:06.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我告戰終
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.67,0:09:08.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我為人也
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.65,0:09:14.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生存! 兩人 生存!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.78,0:09:16.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃驚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.21,0:09:17.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:19.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 很強
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.92,0:09:22.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還行啦 畢竟曾經是亂破師嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.89,0:09:24.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是廢物 發揮了作用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.34,0:09:27.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.43,0:09:28.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多虧 有你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.10,0:09:30.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唔 算是盡了份力…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.95,0:09:33.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重新委託 帶路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.87,0:09:34.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.02,0:09:36.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名字 你?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.88,0:09:39.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托魯 托魯·亞裘拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.55,0:09:41.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.75,0:09:42.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡·賈…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.71,0:09:43.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,訂正
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.58,0:09:45.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡·托勒龐特
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Eyecatch
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.70,0:09:54.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是對不住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.40,0:09:59.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若我能更好地使馭你 你也不至於葬身於此了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.62,0:10:02.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟打敗了棄獸…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.95,0:10:04.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那到底是什麼人物?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.04,0:10:07.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女孩兒應一直是獨自行動的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.85,0:10:10.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得到了協助者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.36,0:10:17.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驚愕的胃袋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.18,0:10:18.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,運動完肚子會特別餓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.62,0:10:21.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且呀 能吃的時候不多吃點…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.03,0:10:24.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你錢夠吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.66,0:10:26.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就無問題啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.68,0:10:30.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什麼在這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.80,0:10:34.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而野菜 又在哪兒…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.19,0:10:37.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本以為你終於肯幹活了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.46,0:10:40.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到沒去挖野菜 而是摘了個少女回來呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.99,0:10:43.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明已經有我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.20,0:10:45.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還和個如此水靈的姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.58,0:10:47.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臉對臉 在這兒坐著吃早餐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.01,0:10:50.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺瀟灑的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.17,0:11:01.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你整天整天也不去工作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.95,0:11:04.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待在家裡無所事事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.07,0:11:07.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全靠我一個人維持家計啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.30,0:11:10.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不該吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.47,0:11:11.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這男的真過分
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.34,0:11:14.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已忍無可忍了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.87,0:11:15.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.28,0:11:18.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 等等 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.16,0:11:19.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,覺悟!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.00,0:11:20.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等阿卡莉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.19,0:11:22.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你誤會了!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.49,0:11:27.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我誤會了什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.60,0:11:30.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小女子愚鈍 還請開示一二吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.25,0:11:31.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.24,0:11:32.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄長?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.33,0:11:33.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄妹?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.01,0:11:38.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 「不稱職的老哥」這個評價是跑不掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.57,0:11:41.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把等候早餐的妹妹忘在腦後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.53,0:11:44.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光顧著自己大吃大喝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.16,0:11:46.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還砸了我的店
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.35,0:11:48.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且無論飯錢還是賠款
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.27,0:11:52.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都丟給剛認識的這女孩付賬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.22,0:11:55.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驚得我連氣都生不出了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.83,0:11:59.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在你身上聞到濃濃的廢柴味道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.35,0:12:02.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受到了棄獸的襲擊?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.09,0:12:05.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這話 我真能相信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.44,0:12:08.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 然後得這丫頭幫助 幹掉了它
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.50,0:12:10.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是魔法師
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.03,0:12:12.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棺材裡放著機杖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.46,0:12:14.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.10,0:12:16.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傷就是戰斗的證據
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.01,0:12:20.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後請客吃飯 就是帶路的謝禮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.99,0:12:21.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.19,0:12:23.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,委託 工作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.29,0:12:27.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要 亂破師兄妹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.00,0:12:28.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.24,0:12:30.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.19,0:12:33.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不會想拒絕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.34,0:12:36.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 可我都多少年沒工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.20,0:12:38.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然要我幹活…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.30,0:12:41.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是去工作 還是被我製成標本
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.32,0:12:43.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請選一條路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.13,0:12:45.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這兩條?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.64,0:12:49.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是說 兄長你希望由我親手製成標本?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.43,0:12:54.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.17,0:12:57.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是不得不工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.24,0:13:09.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎蒞臨寒舍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.25,0:13:12.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是羅伯特·阿巴爾特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.98,0:13:15.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您是叫…亞伯力克·基烈特是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.59,0:13:16.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.39,0:13:18.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您年輕得令人驚訝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.50,0:13:23.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本聽聞來的是克里曼機關的人 我還以為定是位老者呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.71,0:13:26.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說到基烈特家 那可是大大的名門
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.00,0:13:28.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為何要從事這份工作?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.76,0:13:33.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下對自己現在日夜為其奔走的工作感到自豪和責任感 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.30,0:13:35.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 抱歉我問了個失禮的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.50,0:13:37.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了請問 此次造訪所為何事?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.53,0:13:41.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下很清楚我們初次見面此舉顯得十分唐突無禮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.22,0:13:43.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但有一事不得不相求
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.37,0:13:50.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽聞您乃討伐賈茲皇帝的八英雄之一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.77,0:13:51.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.47,0:13:55.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想請您將在賈茲帝國帝都攻防戰一役中得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:13:58.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「戰利品」交予在下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.70,0:14:02.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我將戰利品 返還?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.36,0:14:03.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.39,0:14:05.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請問 為何需要它?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.35,0:14:07.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.69,0:14:10.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恕在下由於事需保密 不能告知您
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.05,0:14:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.16,0:14:14.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送客
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.70,0:14:19.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿巴爾特伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.26,0:14:21.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您的心情我十分理解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.64,0:14:25.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 此問題不僅關係到維馬克王國
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.36,0:14:29.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至攸關整個菲爾畢斯特大陸的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.47,0:14:39.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今要我返還?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.56,0:14:41.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想得美
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.00,0:14:48.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作 不花時間 簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.63,0:14:51.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,領主 阿巴爾特伯爵府邸 襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:52.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並奪取
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.41,0:14:53.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奪什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.77,0:14:55.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.22,0:14:57.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了 我 就能知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.86,0:14:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你腦子沒事兒吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.88,0:15:01.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正常 需要 無論如何都
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.82,0:15:03.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須要做的事情 我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.68,0:15:05.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須要做的事情?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.44,0:15:07.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要做 義務
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.31,0:15:09.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使命 絕對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.51,0:15:11.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使耗費一生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.80,0:15:13.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也要努力完成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.87,0:15:19.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若要襲擊 那還得做很多準備
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.87,0:15:22.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.85,0:15:25.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說伯爵出身武門世家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.51,0:15:28.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但今天實際見面 我感到有點不對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.63,0:15:30.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您的意思是?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.02,0:15:33.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他看起來實在不像一位精通武藝之人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.67,0:15:36.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰後五年 武藝生疏了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.15,0:15:39.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且那宅子 也透著一絲古怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.01,0:15:40.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何處古怪?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.36,0:15:43.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衛兵的數量少得出奇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.91,0:15:46.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以領主府邸來說 警備顯得太鬆懈了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.65,0:15:47.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺令人在意的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.45,0:15:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有那女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.69,0:15:51.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕也是因為知道阿巴爾特伯爵是八英雄之一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.37,0:15:53.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才來到這個城市的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.65,0:15:56.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 得到了協助者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.45,0:15:59.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許會動襲擊伯爵府邸的念頭…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.18,0:16:02.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我去監視嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.66,0:16:03.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.43,0:16:14.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是要偷什麼東西?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.08,0:16:18.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不想說 我們也沒必要追問
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.66,0:16:21.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們做好自己工作就行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.01,0:16:22.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「工作」…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.65,0:16:25.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從兄長你口中聽到 真是有種奇怪的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.84,0:16:30.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起這個 房子西面的情況怎樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.87,0:16:32.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和東面同樣的結構
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.28,0:16:38.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到竟要和領主動手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.99,0:16:41.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄長你怕了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.99,0:16:43.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說誰怕了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.81,0:16:46.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 兄長自然是渾身是膽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.98,0:16:48.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便手無寸鐵一絲不掛赤身裸體
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.43,0:16:53.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也定能勇敢無畏笑迎千軍萬馬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.33,0:16:56.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那從各種意義上來說 都只是個傻子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.31,0:17:03.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是兄長你本人 也絕不允許侮辱我敬愛的兄長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.75,0:17:07.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 傻子應該是你才對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.16,0:17:08.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.16,0:17:09.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「就好」?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.62,0:17:13.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想潛進去好像不是很難
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.50,0:17:18.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但據說宅子的主人是在那賈茲帝都攻防戰中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.51,0:17:21.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為先鋒衝進城堡的勇士之一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.34,0:17:24.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那想必是個不折不扣的武斗派啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.41,0:17:27.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得借助她的魔法力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.47,0:17:31.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說到這個 那丫頭 真的可以信任嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.13,0:17:34.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是委託人啊 還談什麼信任…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.17,0:17:36.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我指的是她作為魔法師的本事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.58,0:17:39.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 那可是貨真價實的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.87,0:17:42.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火焰呀起舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.47,0:17:43.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The Burner
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.57,0:17:56.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麵包 大爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.68,0:17:57.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.96,0:17:58.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我理解了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.03,0:18:05.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衛兵少得有點在意 不過算了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.44,0:18:07.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照商量好的行事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.74,0:18:08.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.37,0:18:12.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.83,0:18:14.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裡面放著機杖是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.13,0:18:16.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,攜入 必然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.04,0:18:37.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.74,0:18:38.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我為鋼也
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.46,0:18:42.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鋼故不怯 鋼故不惑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.03,0:18:46.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦逢敵 盡無一切躊躇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.68,0:18:48.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為滅此兇器也
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.76,0:18:50.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鐵血轉化
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.28,0:18:57.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿卡莉 和托魯一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.80,0:18:58.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.13,0:19:05.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.27,0:19:06.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打開棺材
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.88,0:19:20.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉…真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.81,0:19:30.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.90,0:19:32.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿卡莉 再用力推
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.73,0:19:38.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,累死人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.47,0:19:43.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待遇 不正當
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.73,0:19:46.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 接下來怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.75,0:19:47.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要偷什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.44,0:19:49.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基本能明白 我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.34,0:19:52.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 就是要你讓我們也明白啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.38,0:19:54.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上 就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.54,0:19:59.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Efun Heluste Ru NBelguil Fai Sev
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.63,0:20:02.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顯現吧 探測者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.16,0:20:04.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The Locator
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.93,0:20:14.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重要的東西 宅邸中央
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.25,0:20:16.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散發 青白光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.31,0:20:18.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我們分兩頭行動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.54,0:20:20.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我負責一樓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.63,0:20:22.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿卡莉 你和她負責二樓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.50,0:20:24.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.56,0:20:35.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.79,0:20:50.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.95,0:20:54.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是克里曼機關的手下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.16,0:20:58.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來對白天的鎩羽而歸 很是不滿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.69,0:21:00.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.22,0:21:01.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也罷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.39,0:21:07.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正為難得的寶物無處使用 而感覺稍許無聊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.14,0:21:09.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛賊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.23,0:21:16.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…魔法師?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.49,0:21:22.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可和你們上司那騎士小少爺不同
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.29,0:21:28.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄長
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.62,0:21:33.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要過來 這傢伙是個魔法師
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.72,0:21:34.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法師?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.63,0:21:35.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要露臉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.63,0:21:45.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.38,0:21:47.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.00,0:21:49.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你應該已經死了!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.71,0:23:28.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旅途 終要起程
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.42,0:23:31.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托魯 會認真工作? 一絲不安
